  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK929">
<l>kaḷittāṉaik kāraṇaṅ kāṭṭutal kīḻnīrk </l>
<l> kuḷittāṉait tītturīi yaṟṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Reasoning with a drunkard is like going under water with a torch in search of a drowned man.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
